		<p class="mb-4">
			Görüntüleme, aboneler, ve ürün stoğunu takip et
		</p>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="container-fluid py-2">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-xl-3 col-sm-6 mb-xl-0 mb-4">
			<div class="card">
				<div class="card-header p-2 ps-3">
					<div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
